        "title": "Text 5",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Use the slider to change whether the hand is relaxed or flexed. What do you notice?</p><p>How is this realistic data similar or different from the data from the generator?</p>"
