        "title": "Text 7",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Do you know what block or blocks you would use to do what you want to do?</strong></p><p>Can you make your program work?</p><p>If you&#x27;re not sure how to do it, try these things:</p><ul><li>Talk with another group: do they have ideas about how to make your plan work?</li><li>Look at the class gallery: is any other group trying to do the same thing as you? Maybe you can figure it out together!</li><li>Thinking back to the blocks that you tried last class or earlier today: do any of them do what you want?</li><li>Talk with your teacher or a researcher: what ideas do they have?</li></ul>"
          ]
